## NOBS Agency — The B2B SaaS

FastAPI web app at `~/nobs-agency` on tank, port 8070, systemd service.

AI advertising agency with 5 departments: CEO, Creative, Social Media, Research, Analytics — all backed by Ollama (`llama3.1:8b`).

### Architecture
- `ollama_client.py` — async OllamaClient, 3-attempt retry, exponential backoff
- `task_queue.py` — asyncio queue, 3 workers
- `auth.py` — token verification via `nobsdash.com/api/v1/subscription`
- `departments/` — base.py, ceo.py, creative.py, social.py, research.py, analytics.py
- SQLite (`agency.db`) WAL mode
- CEO orchestration: assign → execute → CEO review → iterate (max 3x, threshold 70/100)

### Key API endpoints
- `POST /api/clients/{id}/onboard` — CEO strategy
- `POST /api/research/industry`, `/competitors`, `/trending`
- `POST /api/social/calendar`, `/hashtags`
- `POST /api/content/{id}/score`
- `GET /api/tasks/{id}/stream` — SSE real-time
- `GET /api/tasks/{id}`

To restart: SSH to tank, kill uvicorn on port 8070, relaunch (no sudo for systemctl).

